WEBVTT

01:43.170 --> 01:46.070
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.120 --> 01:49.009
[Episode 8]

01:49.750 --> 01:50.380
Qianqian.

01:50.410 --> 01:51.180
Say something.

01:53.090 --> 01:54.650
My third toast

01:54.680 --> 01:56.660
is to thank Wen Peng.

01:56.890 --> 01:58.470
Not only did you save

01:58.509 --> 01:59.380
Lu Yan and me,

01:59.400 --> 02:00.280
you even found me

02:00.310 --> 02:01.290
such a nice apartment.

02:01.310 --> 02:02.380
Here, a toast to you.

02:03.320 --> 02:04.220
It's nothing.

02:05.360 --> 02:07.110
Congrats on your new home...

02:07.130 --> 02:08.530
He saved you?

02:08.669 --> 02:09.470
When?

02:09.470 --> 02:11.070
It was at a dinner together

02:11.110 --> 02:12.720
and she was then dating someone

02:12.950 --> 02:13.790
very paranoid,

02:13.830 --> 02:15.130
who came in with a knife.

02:15.350 --> 02:16.070
A knife?

02:16.110 --> 02:17.420
Yeah, thank goodness Wen was around.

02:17.870 --> 02:19.000
Were you hurt?

02:19.150 --> 02:20.640
The two of us weren't hurt.

02:21.510 --> 02:21.940
Wen.

02:21.940 --> 02:23.150
How's your hand?

02:24.550 --> 02:25.030
Much better.

02:25.550 --> 02:26.410
That's good.

02:27.130 --> 02:28.510
I really have to thank you then.

02:28.670 --> 02:30.540
You stepped forward to help

02:30.710 --> 02:31.590
in a dangerous situation.

02:32.190 --> 02:32.940
Here.

02:33.110 --> 02:34.030
That's rare in today's

02:34.070 --> 02:34.710
society.

02:36.600 --> 02:37.570
I've been taking care of her

02:37.600 --> 02:38.770
for the past eight years.

02:39.010 --> 02:40.490
When she needed help,

02:40.530 --> 02:41.710
I was always with her.

02:42.210 --> 02:43.170
So, you're welcome.

02:43.310 --> 02:44.079
Okay, okay.

02:46.010 --> 02:47.140
Guys,

02:47.300 --> 02:48.200
let's eat!

02:48.310 --> 02:49.250
You must be starving.

02:49.280 --> 02:50.250
Come on, eat up.

02:50.270 --> 02:50.970
Eat up.

02:51.010 --> 02:51.570
Eat up.

02:51.590 --> 02:52.310
Lu Yan.

02:52.510 --> 02:53.120
I'll help you get it.

02:53.140 --> 02:53.829
You can't reach here.

02:53.910 --> 02:54.680
I want meat.

02:54.710 --> 02:55.350
Thank you.

02:56.750 --> 02:57.590
Want more juice?

02:58.530 --> 02:59.120
Juice...

02:59.350 --> 03:00.050
I'm good...

03:01.530 --> 03:02.710
Here, have some crab.

03:03.750 --> 03:04.230
Thank you.

03:04.230 --> 03:05.070
Let me help you.

03:05.070 --> 03:05.940
Drink some water.

03:05.960 --> 03:07.170
I'll peel it for you, okay?

03:07.210 --> 03:07.790
Okay.

03:10.510 --> 03:11.730
You can open it

03:11.790 --> 03:13.090
from a spot...

03:23.790 --> 03:25.020
You got a bad crab. I'll get another.

03:25.050 --> 03:25.750
Zhong.

03:25.790 --> 03:26.450
Cheers.

03:26.640 --> 03:27.030
Cheers!

03:27.030 --> 03:27.670
Drinking more?

03:28.240 --> 03:30.579
Honey, leave me alone today.

03:30.860 --> 03:31.829
Let me tell you.

03:32.110 --> 03:34.690
I miss the days when we were in school.

03:34.720 --> 03:35.650
Too spicy?

03:35.790 --> 03:36.400
Right?

03:36.640 --> 03:38.329
Back then, you and I...

03:42.530 --> 03:43.750
My cab's here. I'll get going.

03:43.780 --> 03:44.150
Okay.

03:44.190 --> 03:45.200
-Bye.
-Bye.

03:45.280 --> 03:45.829
Take care.

03:45.860 --> 03:46.829
Be safe!

03:47.590 --> 03:48.030
Bye!

03:48.030 --> 03:48.540
Take care.

03:50.000 --> 03:50.910
Text me when you get home.

03:50.940 --> 03:51.470
Okay!

03:51.500 --> 03:51.980
Bye!

03:52.000 --> 03:52.640
Bye!

03:53.690 --> 03:54.450
Look at you.

03:54.540 --> 03:56.360
Why didn't you wear a scarf?

03:56.390 --> 03:57.079
I'm not cold!

03:57.100 --> 03:57.940
You're dressed too lightly.

03:57.970 --> 03:59.000
Hurry up. Wear it.

04:00.750 --> 04:01.590
Aren't you cold?

04:01.630 --> 04:02.220
No, I'm not.

04:02.630 --> 04:03.170
Okay, okay.

04:03.200 --> 04:03.920
I'll wear it.

04:05.360 --> 04:05.960
Oh, right!

04:05.990 --> 04:06.620
We didn't take

04:06.660 --> 04:07.780
any photos today!

04:07.810 --> 04:08.700
We can do that anytime.

04:08.740 --> 04:10.030
Must we do it today?

04:10.150 --> 04:10.960
Are you kidding?

04:10.990 --> 04:12.310
Today's such a memorable day.

04:12.350 --> 04:13.300
Fine, let's do it.

04:13.330 --> 04:13.870
Jie.

04:13.890 --> 04:14.440
Come here!

04:14.540 --> 04:15.390
Let's take photos together.

04:15.390 --> 04:16.140
Okay, hold him.

04:16.180 --> 04:16.700
I'll hold him.

04:16.720 --> 04:17.390
Come on!

04:18.079 --> 04:19.089
I'll hold it.

04:21.750 --> 04:23.650
One, two.

04:25.310 --> 04:26.050
Good, good.

04:26.300 --> 04:26.900
Good?

04:26.930 --> 04:27.530
Yeah.

04:27.700 --> 04:28.680
I took quite a few.

04:28.720 --> 04:29.150
Take a look.

04:29.330 --> 04:30.210
I'll send it to you later.

04:30.270 --> 04:30.830
Send it to our group chat.

04:30.830 --> 04:31.710
Not bad.

04:31.870 --> 04:32.460
Look.

04:32.480 --> 04:34.400
Is your cab almost here?

04:34.680 --> 04:35.270
Don't fret it.

04:35.290 --> 04:36.220
Go home.

04:36.240 --> 04:37.060
My home's nearby.

04:37.080 --> 04:37.909
I'll get going.

04:37.930 --> 04:38.270
Okay.

04:38.300 --> 04:39.350
Let's hang out at my place sometime!

04:39.430 --> 04:40.250
Bye! Bye!

04:40.610 --> 04:41.370
Bye!

04:42.850 --> 04:43.440
Lu Yan.

04:43.659 --> 04:44.690
Why don't I send you home?

04:46.220 --> 04:48.200
Um, I'm going to the hospital.

04:48.360 --> 04:49.640
I'll send you back.

04:50.480 --> 04:52.220
You're going to the hospital at this time?

04:52.790 --> 04:53.820
To see my dad.

04:55.030 --> 04:56.150
Let me give you a ride.

04:58.060 --> 04:59.070
Wen.

04:59.110 --> 05:00.530
He's drunk. Give us a ride.

05:05.280 --> 05:06.030
My goodness!

05:06.050 --> 05:06.550
Let's go!

05:06.580 --> 05:07.230
Let's go!

05:07.310 --> 05:08.310
Let's go! Go!

05:08.330 --> 05:09.510
We're leaving!

05:11.670 --> 05:12.650
Watch out!

05:12.680 --> 05:13.840
Watch your head!

05:19.320 --> 05:20.120
Bye!

05:28.620 --> 05:29.260
Let's go.

05:59.200 --> 06:00.160
Is Zhong okay?

06:07.520 --> 06:08.340
Have some water.

06:08.870 --> 06:09.670
Thank you, Wen.

06:15.880 --> 06:16.960
What's on your mind?

06:17.320 --> 06:18.190
Nothing.

06:20.130 --> 06:21.270
It's just...

06:22.570 --> 06:24.200
it'd be great if Deng Man were still here.

06:28.140 --> 06:29.300
I remember

06:29.340 --> 06:30.710
the three of you were the closest

06:30.750 --> 06:31.920
in university.

06:31.950 --> 06:33.230
You were inseparable.

06:33.850 --> 06:34.890
Unfortunately...

06:39.170 --> 06:40.780
After Deng Man committed suicide,

06:42.050 --> 06:44.040
Yan was in great shock.

06:45.510 --> 06:46.510
She was so

06:46.510 --> 06:47.590
emotionally unstable.

06:49.370 --> 06:50.610
She almost dropped out of school.

06:51.790 --> 06:52.420
She broke up

06:52.420 --> 06:53.740
with Jiang Chengyi then too.

06:56.700 --> 06:57.850
Speaking of which, I have to

06:57.870 --> 06:58.710
thank you.

07:01.020 --> 07:01.920
For what?

07:02.270 --> 07:03.040
Have you forgotten?

07:03.690 --> 07:05.800
When I was very busy at the end of the semester,

07:06.020 --> 07:07.210
Lu Yan was sick,

07:07.360 --> 07:07.880
and you

07:07.910 --> 07:09.070
helped me look after her for a bit.

07:10.700 --> 07:11.680
It's no problem.

07:12.060 --> 07:13.080
It's what I should've done.

07:18.440 --> 07:19.760
Deng Man's passing

07:20.430 --> 07:21.990
really changed all of us.

07:24.200 --> 07:25.960
I went abroad right after

07:26.280 --> 07:27.640
and was scared to come back for a long time.

07:30.520 --> 07:31.670
Yan must've been even more

07:31.710 --> 07:32.390
traumatized.

07:42.270 --> 07:43.230
Wang Qianqian

07:43.560 --> 07:44.710
and you

07:44.990 --> 07:46.140
seem really close.

07:48.430 --> 07:49.950
She started working here

07:49.970 --> 07:50.860
alone,

07:50.909 --> 07:51.870
without family

07:51.870 --> 07:52.810
or friends.

07:53.020 --> 07:54.520
I guess I'm her...

07:54.990 --> 07:56.390
first friend in the hospital.

07:57.550 --> 07:58.270
That's nice.

07:59.110 --> 08:00.040
It's rare to

08:00.070 --> 08:00.750
make close friends

08:00.770 --> 08:01.570
as an adult.

08:03.910 --> 08:05.190
At first,

08:05.810 --> 08:06.790
it wasn't like that.

08:07.830 --> 08:08.860
Here's our nurse station.

08:08.920 --> 08:09.900
Shift handovers

08:09.950 --> 08:10.910
take place here.

08:10.990 --> 08:12.520
The lounge is back there.

08:12.710 --> 08:13.510
Doctors and nurses

08:13.540 --> 08:14.330
all rest there.

08:14.890 --> 08:15.550
Dr. Lu!

08:15.670 --> 08:16.350
What a coincidence.

08:16.380 --> 08:17.470
Let me introduce

08:17.510 --> 08:18.510
our new nurse,

08:18.530 --> 08:19.330
Wang Qianqian.

08:19.820 --> 08:21.260
Anesthesiologist, Lu Yan.

08:21.770 --> 08:23.240
H-Hello, Dr. Lu.

08:26.000 --> 08:27.490
Can I add you on WeChat?

08:27.590 --> 08:28.150
I hope

08:28.170 --> 08:29.090
I can consult you directly

08:29.120 --> 08:30.430
about work.

08:31.740 --> 08:32.659
I didn't bring my phone.

08:32.690 --> 08:33.460
I'm busy.

08:40.409 --> 08:42.330
Dr. Lu, are you alone?

08:42.960 --> 08:44.190
Let's eat together.

08:47.610 --> 08:48.870
You eat so little?

08:49.150 --> 08:50.320
No wonder you're so thin.

08:54.120 --> 08:55.220
I'm done.

09:15.430 --> 09:17.050
Are you really leaving?

09:17.170 --> 09:18.130
Were you scolded?

09:20.200 --> 09:22.680
I accidentally touched the sterile table

09:22.710 --> 09:24.540
in the operating room today

09:25.490 --> 09:27.470
and was kicked out by the matron.

09:36.400 --> 09:37.480
Matron Qiao

09:37.510 --> 09:39.270
seems to have a good temper,

09:40.270 --> 09:42.360
but she's very strict with work.

09:43.810 --> 09:45.130
It's normal to be scolded by her.

09:45.740 --> 09:46.810
Everyone's been scolded at least once.

09:46.840 --> 09:48.400
I'm not crying

09:48.870 --> 09:50.640
because I was scolded.

09:51.290 --> 09:52.750
If the patient

09:52.790 --> 09:54.610
got infected because of me,

09:55.660 --> 09:56.980
what should I've done?

10:04.570 --> 10:06.540
In our line of work,

10:07.640 --> 10:09.580
mistakes cannot be tolerated.

10:09.890 --> 10:11.600
A tiny mistake

10:11.860 --> 10:14.030
could lead to unimaginable consequences.

10:14.330 --> 10:15.860
If you aren't sure, ask more

10:16.040 --> 10:16.840
and look around more.

10:18.620 --> 10:19.350
Then I...

10:22.470 --> 10:23.400
You'll definitely become

10:23.430 --> 10:24.590
an excellent nurse.

10:26.110 --> 10:26.930
Really?

10:32.540 --> 10:33.550
Dr. Lu.

10:36.550 --> 10:38.260
Stay with me a little longer.

10:42.170 --> 10:42.790
Sure.

10:43.750 --> 10:45.540
Can I lean on you?

10:48.410 --> 10:48.920
Okay.

10:55.450 --> 10:56.870
Qianqian always says

10:58.190 --> 10:59.430
I've been taking care of her

10:59.450 --> 11:00.290
and accompanying her.

11:01.870 --> 11:03.560
But she doesn't know that she was the one

11:03.830 --> 11:05.150
who got me out of a slump

11:05.170 --> 11:06.650
that lasted for years.

11:09.340 --> 11:10.550
I'm really grateful to her.

11:21.600 --> 11:22.130
Here!

11:22.630 --> 11:23.380
What is it?

11:23.410 --> 11:24.070
Look.

11:24.780 --> 11:26.510
You brought so much yummy stuff again?

11:26.700 --> 11:27.730
There's one more thing.

11:27.760 --> 11:29.060
What is it?

11:31.590 --> 11:32.340
A scarf?

11:32.360 --> 11:33.800
Yes, it's a gift for you.

11:33.810 --> 11:34.440
Do you like it?

11:34.550 --> 11:34.980
Yes.

11:35.160 --> 11:35.790
Wear it now.

11:37.470 --> 11:38.320
It's so warm.

11:38.360 --> 11:39.380
So beautiful.

11:39.510 --> 11:40.510
It suits you really well.

11:40.590 --> 11:41.180
What do you think?

11:41.430 --> 11:42.010
Nice.

11:42.270 --> 11:42.950
Yeah?

11:43.030 --> 11:43.510
Hurry up.

11:43.550 --> 11:44.110
Are you cold?

11:44.130 --> 11:45.380
No, I'm wearing this.

11:45.410 --> 11:46.070
Okay.

11:46.720 --> 11:48.580
Your favorite strawberry cake.

12:15.910 --> 12:16.510
What's wrong?

12:18.900 --> 12:19.670
Stop the car.

12:24.640 --> 12:25.120
Lu Yan!

12:28.160 --> 12:29.010
Where are you going?

12:34.620 --> 12:35.410
What's wrong?

12:38.900 --> 12:39.280
I...

12:39.310 --> 12:40.080
What are you looking at?

12:41.510 --> 12:42.030
I...

12:42.550 --> 12:44.010
I saw Deng Man.

12:46.280 --> 12:48.030
This is my second time.

12:48.070 --> 12:48.960
Half a month ago,

12:49.000 --> 12:50.420
I saw her once too.

12:53.070 --> 12:53.750
Are you sure?

12:54.910 --> 12:56.220
She was right in front of me,

12:56.250 --> 12:57.020
in the alley

12:57.040 --> 12:58.290
by my apartment building.

12:59.320 --> 13:01.190
Could it just be a look-alike?

13:01.590 --> 13:02.280
Impossible.

13:02.310 --> 13:03.550
I couldn't have been mistaken.

13:04.250 --> 13:05.160
Also...

13:06.450 --> 13:07.660
I was being stalked.

13:20.780 --> 13:22.020
When did that happen?

13:22.860 --> 13:23.510
Just...

13:25.030 --> 13:26.160
Two days ago,

13:27.270 --> 13:28.800
someone kept following me.

13:28.950 --> 13:30.500
I hid in the fruit shop.

13:30.580 --> 13:31.240
And then

13:31.710 --> 13:32.510
they disappeared

13:32.550 --> 13:33.430
when I came out.

13:38.400 --> 13:39.320
Give me your phone.

13:54.020 --> 13:55.350
I'll set my number

13:55.580 --> 13:57.220
as your emergency contact.

13:57.790 --> 13:59.200
When you're in danger,

13:59.390 --> 14:00.660
just press the dial key

14:00.990 --> 14:01.630
to call me.

14:07.390 --> 14:07.950
Okay.

14:12.470 --> 14:13.110
Get in the car.

14:15.270 --> 14:15.750
Let's go.

14:33.040 --> 14:35.110
I understand Jiang Chengyi,

14:35.190 --> 14:36.080
but why was Wen

14:36.110 --> 14:36.790
so weird too?

14:40.310 --> 14:41.430
Look at the time!

14:42.190 --> 14:42.790
Honey.

14:42.820 --> 14:43.650
I drank too much yesterday.

14:43.710 --> 14:44.950
Let me sleep a little longer.

14:45.120 --> 14:45.910
Get up now.

14:45.940 --> 14:46.670
Hurry up.

14:46.670 --> 14:47.590
Please.

14:47.600 --> 14:48.840
Just a bit longer.

14:50.040 --> 14:51.120
Are you free today?

14:51.270 --> 14:52.040
Yes.

14:52.070 --> 14:53.110
Dalu's handling the work today.

14:55.190 --> 14:56.310
Go somewhere with me.

14:58.700 --> 14:59.830
Go somewhere with me!

14:59.950 --> 15:01.980
What for?

15:02.190 --> 15:02.950
Let's have a date.

15:05.110 --> 15:06.120
Where are we going, honey?

15:07.480 --> 15:08.500
You'll see.

15:14.350 --> 15:15.050
Lu.

15:15.150 --> 15:16.160
Going for a run again?

15:20.530 --> 15:21.150
Forget running.

15:21.230 --> 15:22.230
Let's go eat something good.

15:22.270 --> 15:22.750
What's this?

15:22.750 --> 15:23.550
You've been kidnapped by us.

15:23.580 --> 15:23.950
Let's go.

15:23.990 --> 15:24.910
I'm not going!

15:31.550 --> 15:33.110
Dr. Lu, you're so self-disciplined.

15:33.340 --> 15:34.500
You don't drink at all.

15:36.200 --> 15:36.990
Tell me.

15:37.270 --> 15:38.380
What’s up?

15:42.270 --> 15:42.920
Lu Yan.

15:43.380 --> 15:44.570
I have good news

15:44.590 --> 15:46.000
that I think I should tell you.

15:47.750 --> 15:49.190
Jiang Chengyi is back.

15:50.030 --> 15:52.370
He was transferred to the Anshan Criminal Investigation Unit.

15:53.000 --> 15:53.800
Surprised?

15:53.980 --> 15:55.100
Shocked?

15:58.350 --> 15:59.510
I don't think she understood

15:59.510 --> 16:00.330
what I said.

16:00.520 --> 16:01.190
Yeah.

16:01.190 --> 16:01.630
Aren't you

16:01.660 --> 16:03.030
too calm about it?

16:03.230 --> 16:04.180
I know about it.

16:04.500 --> 16:05.480
You do?

16:08.070 --> 16:08.670
Impossible.

16:09.550 --> 16:10.510
Absolutely impossible.

16:10.600 --> 16:11.040
Honey.

16:11.090 --> 16:12.260
I guarantee

16:12.290 --> 16:13.430
I was the first to know

16:13.470 --> 16:14.620
that Jiang Chengyi came back.

16:14.870 --> 16:15.310
Jiang and I—

16:15.310 --> 16:15.870
Zhong.

16:16.340 --> 16:17.930
I doubt you're even in his top three.

16:19.680 --> 16:20.750
Fine.

16:20.780 --> 16:22.710
You two having a secret liaison?

16:22.810 --> 16:23.560
Stop eating.

16:23.590 --> 16:24.740
Tell us what happened.

16:25.030 --> 16:25.750
Well,

16:25.850 --> 16:27.650
his dad had an operation at our hospital.

16:29.350 --> 16:30.430
We...

16:31.910 --> 16:33.110
just chatted a bit.

16:36.490 --> 16:37.220
Lu Yan.

16:37.930 --> 16:38.800
If Jiang Chengyi

16:38.830 --> 16:40.770
didn't come back to get back with you,

16:40.980 --> 16:42.660
I'll hand you Zhong's head on a platter.

16:42.680 --> 16:43.230
Honey—

16:43.260 --> 16:44.790
Why would I want his head?

16:45.150 --> 16:46.820
He came back to see his dad.

16:47.080 --> 16:48.060
He said it himself.

16:49.110 --> 16:49.750
I swear.

16:50.910 --> 16:51.870
Swear?

16:52.190 --> 16:52.630
Fine.

16:52.640 --> 16:53.550
You two just keep lying

16:53.590 --> 16:54.230
to yourselves.

16:55.750 --> 16:57.190
Was this why you kidnapped me here?

16:58.550 --> 16:59.550
Not only this.

17:00.750 --> 17:01.360
Well...

17:01.650 --> 17:02.850
What's going on with Wen?

17:04.200 --> 17:04.839
Who?

17:04.869 --> 17:05.859
Wen.

17:06.150 --> 17:07.050
Wen?

17:07.240 --> 17:07.849
Yeah!

17:08.060 --> 17:08.920
Don't you think

17:08.990 --> 17:09.910
he was too nice to you

17:10.180 --> 17:10.970
and even

17:11.180 --> 17:12.250
wary of Jiang Chengyi

17:12.280 --> 17:12.839
last night?

17:13.140 --> 17:13.670
Honey.

17:13.690 --> 17:14.450
Why didn't I notice?

17:14.480 --> 17:15.329
You were drunk.

17:15.390 --> 17:16.190
Do you even remember

17:16.190 --> 17:16.790
how you got home?

17:17.510 --> 17:19.010
Wen...

17:19.109 --> 17:20.650
seems to have been a bit...

17:20.869 --> 17:21.829
weird lately.

17:23.050 --> 17:24.440
Does he like you?

17:25.569 --> 17:26.750
No way.

17:26.859 --> 17:28.640
Ever since he quit as a doctor,

17:28.830 --> 17:29.390
we haven't

17:29.390 --> 17:30.530
been in touch.

17:30.670 --> 17:31.750
I only see him...

17:32.910 --> 17:33.630
at gatherings

17:33.630 --> 17:35.470
during festivals and such.

17:36.190 --> 17:37.400
You two were present too!

17:38.550 --> 17:39.350
That's true.

17:39.790 --> 17:40.740
Then what's going on?

17:43.850 --> 17:44.870
I know.

17:45.360 --> 17:46.470
It's not about you.

17:46.500 --> 17:48.180
It's about Jiang Chengyi.

17:48.290 --> 17:49.200
Didn’t you see?

17:49.310 --> 17:50.630
Whenever Jiang Chengyi was nice to you,

17:50.650 --> 17:51.310
he got angry.

17:51.320 --> 17:52.630
Whenever Jiang Chengyi was nice to you, he got angry.

17:52.790 --> 17:53.350
Whenever—

17:53.630 --> 17:54.550
Eat your food.

17:55.270 --> 17:55.950
Get your mind

17:55.990 --> 17:57.490
out of the gutter.

17:59.910 --> 18:00.470
Lu Yan.

18:01.080 --> 18:02.130
Be honest.

18:02.390 --> 18:03.630
How do you feel

18:03.670 --> 18:04.990
about Jiang Chengyi now?

18:10.950 --> 18:12.030
I've visited him in Jinzhou

18:12.050 --> 18:13.300
over the years.

18:13.820 --> 18:14.430
Think about it.

18:14.450 --> 18:15.070
He used to

18:15.150 --> 18:17.000
be such a lively person.

18:17.270 --> 18:18.780
Ever since you broke up,

18:18.910 --> 18:20.030
it was like he became another person,

18:20.150 --> 18:21.420
all cold and detached.

18:21.870 --> 18:23.450
I often teased him,

18:23.760 --> 18:25.360
saying he's completely changed

18:25.520 --> 18:27.150
after becoming a cop,

18:27.510 --> 18:28.390
that he's one of them now.

18:29.360 --> 18:30.570
Actually, I know

18:30.600 --> 18:32.130
that's not who he is.

18:32.450 --> 18:34.040
Ever since you two broke up,

18:34.070 --> 18:36.150
he's been so miserable.

18:36.620 --> 18:37.690
He's like a living zombie.

18:39.350 --> 18:40.320
He always

18:40.350 --> 18:42.220
went for the most dangerous missions,

18:43.230 --> 18:44.470
like he didn't care for his life.

18:47.630 --> 18:48.320
Then...

18:50.570 --> 18:52.060
Has he ever been injured?

18:56.380 --> 18:57.800
What do you think?

18:58.240 --> 18:59.270
Whenever I visited him,

18:59.290 --> 19:00.440
he was always wounded.

19:00.990 --> 19:02.170
How do you think he got

19:02.270 --> 19:02.900
all his awards?

19:02.950 --> 19:04.320
He risked his life every time.

19:04.510 --> 19:05.200
But he's different

19:05.230 --> 19:06.400
after meeting you here.

19:06.430 --> 19:08.110
There's light in his eyes again,

19:08.150 --> 19:09.440
like he was revived.

19:10.710 --> 19:11.430
Lu Yan,

19:12.340 --> 19:13.450
our great Dr. Lu,

19:14.890 --> 19:15.640
please help out

19:16.150 --> 19:17.070
and save Jiang.

19:21.740 --> 19:22.390
Lu Yan.

19:23.220 --> 19:25.220
If you really don't plan to do that,

19:25.370 --> 19:26.480
then let him go.

19:26.510 --> 19:27.580
Don't give him hope.

19:28.050 --> 19:28.980
That's enough.

19:29.630 --> 19:30.190
Don't pressure

19:30.230 --> 19:30.940
Yan like that.

19:31.030 --> 19:32.040
What pressure?

19:32.070 --> 19:33.070
What I mean is

19:33.150 --> 19:34.550
if Lu saves Jiang,

19:34.830 --> 19:35.410
it'll be a miracle

19:35.440 --> 19:36.350
greater than becoming immortal!

19:36.430 --> 19:37.550
Huh? What?

19:38.380 --> 19:39.310
Do you think Yan has

19:39.330 --> 19:40.020
had it easy?

19:40.100 --> 19:41.160
She's not acting like him

19:41.230 --> 19:42.230
like it's the end of the world,

19:42.750 --> 19:43.510
but wasn't she

19:43.510 --> 19:44.580
devastated that day too?

19:44.670 --> 19:45.720
That's even better!

19:45.750 --> 19:47.190
Mutual redemption! A perfect match!

19:47.210 --> 19:48.200
Enough already.

19:48.410 --> 19:49.320
I'm still here.

19:49.350 --> 19:50.250
Stop acting.

19:50.400 --> 19:51.620
Eat up and let's leave.

19:52.960 --> 19:53.570
Eat up.

19:56.830 --> 19:58.660
I'm just doing this for my buddy.

20:01.710 --> 20:02.430
Well...

20:04.630 --> 20:06.580
Were his injuries serious?

20:28.920 --> 20:29.580
Coming.

20:30.330 --> 20:31.200
You're quick.

20:31.230 --> 20:31.990
Dalu's here too.

20:32.020 --> 20:32.960
Of course.

20:33.510 --> 20:34.110
Boss Zhong

20:34.130 --> 20:35.260
took me out for some fresh air.

20:35.420 --> 20:36.960
Don't you know all pets must be on leash?

20:36.990 --> 20:37.790
You'll get fined.

20:37.810 --> 20:38.640
Don't worry.

20:38.660 --> 20:39.450
The leash is in the car.

20:40.200 --> 20:41.470
Cut the crap. What's up?

20:41.490 --> 20:42.450
Jiang Chengyi.

20:42.760 --> 20:43.510
You'll regret

20:43.550 --> 20:44.920
speaking to me in that tone.

20:45.170 --> 20:46.040
Have I ever

20:46.070 --> 20:46.870
regretted it?

20:48.630 --> 20:49.470
Today,

20:49.550 --> 20:50.920
my dear wife Tang Jie and I

20:51.040 --> 20:52.070
went to see Lu Yan.

20:52.390 --> 20:52.970
I

20:53.000 --> 20:53.800
told Lu Yan

20:53.830 --> 20:55.090
about how miserable you've been

20:55.270 --> 20:56.510
all this while.

20:59.500 --> 21:00.870
Why did you tell her that?

21:01.520 --> 21:02.150
I...

21:05.830 --> 21:07.100
Jiang.

21:07.700 --> 21:09.660
You're too headstrong.

21:09.730 --> 21:10.690
Listen.

21:11.100 --> 21:12.230
Girls nowadays

21:13.710 --> 21:15.000
aren't that into macho

21:15.030 --> 21:16.350
old wolf dogs like you.

21:16.490 --> 21:18.050
You're the old wolf dog.

21:18.260 --> 21:19.420
It's true.

21:19.500 --> 21:20.970
Puppy-like guys who can be

21:21.000 --> 21:22.800
cute and vulnerable are all the rage.

21:22.870 --> 21:23.350
That's right.

21:23.430 --> 21:24.430
I won Tang Jie's heart

21:24.450 --> 21:25.600
with this trick.

21:26.260 --> 21:27.180
See?

21:27.670 --> 21:28.340
How loving.

21:28.430 --> 21:29.080
E-Enough.

21:29.110 --> 21:29.990
You bulldog.

21:31.670 --> 21:32.750
W-What did she say?

21:40.610 --> 21:41.990
Buddy.

21:43.010 --> 21:45.360
The best buddy in the world.

21:45.680 --> 21:46.530
Being vulnerable?

21:47.050 --> 21:48.200
That's more like it.

21:48.230 --> 21:50.420
If you don't want to be punched in your face,

21:50.530 --> 21:51.870
get to the point.

21:55.260 --> 21:56.410
She didn't say anything.

21:57.180 --> 21:57.910
But I could

21:57.950 --> 21:59.270
tell from her eyes

21:59.310 --> 22:00.740
that she really cares about you.

22:01.350 --> 22:02.000
I think she

22:02.070 --> 22:02.830
hasn't let you go.

22:03.610 --> 22:05.430
Now that you're back,

22:06.130 --> 22:07.600
why don't you strike while the iron's hot?

22:07.650 --> 22:09.010
She's almost 30 years old.

22:09.110 --> 22:10.120
She might go on some blind date

22:10.150 --> 22:11.570
and before you know it,

22:11.590 --> 22:13.230
she's married with four kids.

22:13.600 --> 22:14.280
Shut up.

22:14.300 --> 22:15.180
How could it be so quick?

22:15.550 --> 22:16.430
You'd better stay out

22:16.480 --> 22:17.160
of this.

22:17.880 --> 22:19.000
If I didn't get involved,

22:19.030 --> 22:20.500
you might really have no hope.

22:21.320 --> 22:22.760
You'll regret refusing the help

22:22.810 --> 22:23.390
of such a

22:23.420 --> 22:24.490
brilliant love coach like me.

22:25.380 --> 22:26.980
Is there so much to regret about?

22:27.000 --> 22:27.660
Hey.

22:28.770 --> 22:30.540
Aren't you going to strategize?

22:30.670 --> 22:31.600
Strategize?

22:32.190 --> 22:32.830
I do

22:32.850 --> 22:34.270
enough of that at work.

22:36.030 --> 22:37.620
Here's an important lead for you.

22:38.010 --> 22:39.590
She runs at the riverside park

22:40.110 --> 22:40.910
in her neighborhood

22:40.930 --> 22:41.890
every day after work.

22:42.920 --> 22:43.790
That's it?

22:46.130 --> 22:47.520
That's none of my business.

22:47.870 --> 22:48.530
Bye.

22:48.790 --> 22:49.570
Really leaving?

22:51.310 --> 22:52.490
Be careful on your operations!

22:54.160 --> 22:55.030
I bet two yuan

22:55.080 --> 22:56.140
that he's just acting tough.

22:56.160 --> 22:56.840
I'll up it.

22:56.880 --> 22:57.600
I bet three yuan

22:57.630 --> 22:58.530
that he'll regret it soon.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.710
[Moka Bros]

23:29.700 --> 23:30.770
Jiang Chengyi.

23:32.510 --> 23:33.100
What are you doing?

23:33.120 --> 23:34.270
What are you doing here?

23:34.580 --> 23:35.460
Waiting for you.

23:36.420 --> 23:37.310
Waiting for me?

23:37.360 --> 23:38.260
Are you on a run?

23:40.070 --> 23:40.860
Let's run together.

23:41.240 --> 23:41.910
Sure.

23:42.320 --> 23:43.340
What are you listening to?

23:43.400 --> 23:44.050
Let me listen.

23:49.680 --> 23:52.110
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

23:53.650 --> 23:56.120
♫Romance only exists with you♫

23:57.050 --> 23:59.170
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

24:00.100 --> 24:03.810
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

24:04.600 --> 24:07.410
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

24:08.490 --> 24:10.630
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

24:12.090 --> 24:15.370
♫Endless loving and longing♫

24:19.450 --> 24:20.510
Jiang Chengyi?

24:22.880 --> 24:23.910
Jiang Chengyi!

24:26.630 --> 24:27.510
What are you

24:27.750 --> 24:28.670
doing here?

24:29.570 --> 24:30.830
I-I-I...

24:31.420 --> 24:32.240
I'm running.

24:33.320 --> 24:34.480
You...

24:34.810 --> 24:36.320
run in this area?

24:37.020 --> 24:37.500
Yeah.

24:37.530 --> 24:39.180
I went to...

24:39.220 --> 24:40.130
visit my dad.

24:40.160 --> 24:41.950
Then I wanted to exercise.

24:41.970 --> 24:42.930
So I...

24:42.960 --> 24:44.280
came here to exercise.

24:44.830 --> 24:45.550
Are you...

24:46.070 --> 24:46.840
running?

24:47.990 --> 24:48.580
Yeah.

24:49.490 --> 24:50.070
Oh, right,

24:50.090 --> 24:51.420
you know your dad can be discharged

24:51.440 --> 24:52.230
tomorrow, yeah?

24:53.540 --> 24:54.610
I-I know.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.280
Tomorrow, I...

24:56.350 --> 24:57.110
I have work to do.

24:57.110 --> 24:58.060
And then...

24:58.800 --> 24:59.970
I'll come here in advance

25:00.170 --> 25:01.150
to pack his stuff.

25:01.650 --> 25:02.190
Okay.

25:02.500 --> 25:03.070
Then

25:03.090 --> 25:04.030
I'll continue running.

25:04.240 --> 25:04.850
Go ahead.

25:07.720 --> 25:08.500
Lu Yan.

25:11.460 --> 25:12.570
Let's run together.

25:13.550 --> 25:14.510
I'm super slow.

25:14.670 --> 25:15.870
I can't catch up with you.

25:15.900 --> 25:17.150
It's okay. I'll slow down.

25:17.700 --> 25:18.310
Okay.

25:18.870 --> 25:19.750
What are you listening to?

25:21.240 --> 25:22.000
Want to listen?

25:22.110 --> 25:22.710
Sure.

25:22.990 --> 25:23.670
Are you sure?

25:26.590 --> 25:27.590
Take it then.

25:34.790 --> 25:35.720
Hello, everyone.

25:35.740 --> 25:36.730
Welcome to

25:36.770 --> 25:38.390
today's podcast.

25:38.890 --> 25:40.230
On September 20,

25:40.260 --> 25:41.700
a surgeon from

25:41.730 --> 25:43.390
the University of Maryland Medical Center

25:43.420 --> 25:44.420
successfully transplanted

25:44.470 --> 25:45.230
a transgenic pig heart...

25:45.230 --> 25:46.230
What the hell is this?

25:46.230 --> 25:47.500
Into a human body.

26:00.650 --> 26:02.010
Someone said

26:02.030 --> 26:03.360
to let nature take its course

26:03.520 --> 26:05.420
but ended up listening to a story about a pig's heart.

26:05.770 --> 26:06.500
So?

26:06.650 --> 26:08.330
Regret not listening to me now?

26:08.810 --> 26:09.600
Cut the crap.

26:09.630 --> 26:11.140
Just tell me what to do.

26:11.190 --> 26:12.380
Listen.

26:12.410 --> 26:15.430
You made a grave mistake today.

26:15.450 --> 26:17.240
Couldn't you've been honest?

26:17.370 --> 26:18.900
Why did you say you ran into her

26:18.930 --> 26:20.410
by coincidence?

26:20.430 --> 26:21.600
So unromantic.

26:21.800 --> 26:22.870
What should I have said?

26:23.030 --> 26:23.760
Tell her

26:23.790 --> 26:24.790
I went there

26:24.840 --> 26:25.600
to wait for her?

26:25.830 --> 26:27.280
That's so pressurizing.

26:27.300 --> 26:28.330
Bro,

26:28.790 --> 26:30.080
girls want to

26:30.110 --> 26:31.730
be the exception.

26:31.910 --> 26:33.540
Forget about all that by chance,

26:33.590 --> 26:34.080
coincidence,

26:34.110 --> 26:35.430
and happenstance, okay?

26:36.110 --> 26:36.730
Fine.

26:36.840 --> 26:39.020
Let me teach you a foolproof move.

26:39.270 --> 26:40.510
Take her to

26:40.770 --> 26:41.590
a very romantic

26:41.710 --> 26:43.310
and classy restaurant.

26:44.180 --> 26:46.340
It's better if you can see the night view.

26:46.450 --> 26:47.180
Have a drink together.

26:49.310 --> 26:49.790
Huh...

26:50.220 --> 26:52.180
Isn't that too grand of a gesture?

26:53.560 --> 26:56.210
Take her to dinner right now!

26:57.790 --> 26:59.400
How can I ask her out?

26:59.790 --> 27:00.430
Jiang.

27:00.790 --> 27:01.910
Have you forgotten

27:01.910 --> 27:02.590
how you courted her

27:02.630 --> 27:03.380
in school?

27:03.470 --> 27:04.990
Are you so prideful now?

27:05.690 --> 27:06.490
No.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.990
She courted me back then.

27:14.560 --> 27:16.450
He's hopeless.

27:24.250 --> 27:25.300
Are you asleep?

27:34.780 --> 27:35.600
No.

27:35.710 --> 27:36.300
What's up?

27:38.660 --> 27:43.610
[No. What's up?]

27:49.990 --> 27:51.220
Nothing.

27:51.390 --> 27:53.870
I'm just asking if you're home.

27:57.870 --> 27:59.510
If I'm home?

28:01.990 --> 28:03.310
If I'm home?

28:08.010 --> 28:08.400
Mm,

28:08.420 --> 28:08.950
I'm home.

28:19.630 --> 28:21.640
Let me teach you a foolproof move.

28:22.130 --> 28:23.360
Take her to

28:23.610 --> 28:24.510
a very romantic

28:24.540 --> 28:26.220
and classy restaurant.

28:35.560 --> 28:38.290
-Want to hang out this weekend?
-Are you free this weekend?

28:53.510 --> 28:55.360
I know of a nice restaurant.

28:56.750 --> 28:57.990
My friend recommended

28:57.990 --> 28:59.070
a good restaurant.

28:59.430 --> 29:01.190
Do you want to try it?

29:04.400 --> 29:05.660
That sounds so dumb.

29:19.860 --> 29:20.990
Are you free this weekend?

29:21.310 --> 29:22.760
Let's grab a meal together.

29:22.830 --> 29:24.830
Let's grab a meal together sometime.

29:27.210 --> 29:28.460
[Video Call] [Voice Call]

29:28.720 --> 29:28.890
[Lu Yan: Are you free this weekend? Let's grab a meal together.]

29:28.720 --> 29:28.890
[Jiang Chengyi: Let's grab a meal together sometime.]

29:28.890 --> 29:29.650
[Calling]

29:41.850 --> 29:42.920
Um...

29:43.830 --> 29:45.170
if you're free this weekend,

29:45.990 --> 29:47.100
want to grab a meal together?

29:51.940 --> 29:52.780
Sure.

29:53.260 --> 29:53.800
Okay.

29:53.960 --> 29:55.190
I'll make reservations

29:55.190 --> 29:56.030
and text you the info.

30:00.990 --> 30:01.920
Good night. Bye.

30:02.200 --> 30:02.970
Good night.

30:44.820 --> 30:46.000
How about this?

30:48.380 --> 30:50.260
It's too boxy. No, no.

30:50.980 --> 30:51.800
How's this?

30:53.930 --> 30:56.170
Why's there a skirt attached?

31:00.750 --> 31:02.270
What was I thinking?

31:02.270 --> 31:03.270
Why did I even buy this?

31:11.830 --> 31:12.740
Are you up?

31:12.780 --> 31:14.510
Can I pick you up at 11?

31:16.440 --> 31:17.240
No problem.

31:19.850 --> 31:21.240
Hurry up. Hurry up.

31:21.240 --> 31:21.720
Hurry up.

31:23.020 --> 31:24.000
Which one's better?

31:26.930 --> 31:28.090
What am I doing?

31:29.030 --> 31:30.500
This is not a date.

31:30.880 --> 31:31.510
I...

31:31.830 --> 31:33.720
I'll just wear anything.

31:33.780 --> 31:34.370
This...

31:34.430 --> 31:35.700
They're all nice.

31:35.910 --> 31:36.830
I'll wear a trench coat.

31:36.850 --> 31:37.820
It's more elegant.

31:45.410 --> 31:46.570
Is he here already?

31:48.250 --> 31:49.730
Didn't we agree

31:49.790 --> 31:50.850
on 11 o'clock...

31:50.870 --> 31:52.130
What 11 o'clock?

31:54.070 --> 31:55.080
Oh, Huang Wei.

31:56.450 --> 31:57.220
What's wrong?

31:57.710 --> 31:58.900
I know you're off today,

31:58.930 --> 32:00.510
but there's been a surge of patients in the ER.

32:00.710 --> 32:01.760
Can you come?

32:02.160 --> 32:02.960
N-No problem.

32:03.030 --> 32:04.100
I'll be right there.

32:16.960 --> 32:17.680
Hello?

32:17.950 --> 32:19.510
There's a patient at the ER

32:19.510 --> 32:20.510
I need to check on.

32:20.910 --> 32:22.150
It's okay. I'll wait for you.

32:22.850 --> 32:23.980
It might take a while.

32:24.030 --> 32:25.750
You have to eat no matter how late it is.

32:26.160 --> 32:27.190
If it doesn't work,

32:27.230 --> 32:27.950
we can have supper.

32:28.470 --> 32:29.420
I'm so sorry.

32:29.980 --> 32:30.540
It's okay.

32:30.560 --> 32:31.350
Go ahead.

32:31.370 --> 32:32.600
I'll get back to work.

32:32.630 --> 32:33.230
Bye.

32:47.020 --> 32:47.830
Hello, sir.

32:47.850 --> 32:48.860
How may I help you?

32:50.590 --> 32:52.070
Can you wrap up

32:52.440 --> 32:53.560
this gray scarf for me?

32:53.580 --> 32:54.230
Sure.

32:55.830 --> 32:57.360
Is it for your girlfriend?

32:58.760 --> 32:59.430
Yes.

32:59.700 --> 33:01.640
Then I'd recommend another

33:01.670 --> 33:02.690
dark gray scarf too.

33:02.870 --> 33:03.620
They're our

33:03.670 --> 33:05.230
best-selling pair for couples.

33:05.430 --> 33:06.480
For couples?

33:07.160 --> 33:08.000
Sure, okay.

33:08.350 --> 33:09.010
Wrap it up too.

33:09.190 --> 33:09.830
Okay, a moment, please.

33:09.850 --> 33:10.310
Okay.

33:16.270 --> 33:16.870
Hello?

33:17.430 --> 33:18.100
Jiang.

33:18.180 --> 33:18.910
We're going to bust

33:18.950 --> 33:19.750
an illegal den.

33:19.770 --> 33:20.600
We need backup.

33:21.440 --> 33:22.350
Text me the location.

33:22.390 --> 33:23.380
I'll be right there.

33:27.990 --> 33:28.570
Lu Yan.

33:28.600 --> 33:29.510
I have an urgent mission.

33:29.550 --> 33:30.550
I'll call you later.

33:33.560 --> 33:35.800
[Public Security]

33:38.020 --> 33:38.740
[Police]

34:01.000 --> 34:01.660
Freeze!

34:01.690 --> 34:02.790
Stop there! Freeze!

34:03.600 --> 34:04.220
Freeze!

34:04.240 --> 34:05.600
-Get down!
-Get down!

34:05.640 --> 34:06.270
Behave!

34:06.270 --> 34:07.000
Get down!

34:07.790 --> 34:08.590
Freeze! Police!

34:08.659 --> 34:09.540
Freeze! Police!

34:21.190 --> 34:22.400
Freeze! Get down!

34:22.860 --> 34:23.460
Freeze!

34:24.270 --> 34:25.010
Freeze!

34:38.810 --> 34:40.090
Captain, there's a situation down here.

34:44.870 --> 34:45.480
Freeze!

35:30.620 --> 35:31.220
Lu Yan.

35:31.290 --> 35:32.310
I have an urgent mission.

35:32.330 --> 35:33.240
I'll call you later.

35:34.610 --> 35:35.390
No hurry.

35:35.410 --> 35:37.610
I'll wait for you at the restaurant.

35:58.160 --> 36:00.640
[Low Battery]

36:07.870 --> 36:08.470
Miss.

36:08.550 --> 36:09.280
Our restaurant

36:09.310 --> 36:10.280
is closing soon.

36:10.300 --> 36:11.490
Is your friend not here yet?

36:15.080 --> 36:15.840
Okay.

36:53.870 --> 36:54.390
Listen.

36:54.410 --> 36:55.050
You've no idea

36:55.070 --> 36:56.100
how cool Captain was today.

36:56.120 --> 36:56.860
With his pose—

36:56.950 --> 36:57.470
bam, pow!

36:57.490 --> 36:58.220
They were scared

36:58.250 --> 36:58.690
witless!

36:58.750 --> 36:59.460
I'm leaving!

36:59.480 --> 37:00.420
Where are you going?

37:00.510 --> 37:02.000
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

37:00.880 --> 37:02.050
I haven't thanked you yet.

37:02.080 --> 37:02.830
For what?

37:02.900 --> 37:03.970
For troubling you.

37:03.990 --> 37:05.340
We've been eyeing them for so long,

37:05.430 --> 37:06.710
and every time we tried to catch them,

37:06.730 --> 37:07.590
they got away.

37:07.630 --> 37:08.820
But you caught them all!

37:08.920 --> 37:09.980
It's my duty.

37:10.330 --> 37:10.840
I’ll get going.

37:10.870 --> 37:11.270
Captain Jiang.

37:11.920 --> 37:12.920
Let's get supper.

37:13.000 --> 37:14.040
No thanks. You guys go.

37:14.060 --> 37:14.490
No.

37:14.520 --> 37:15.920
It's my treat. We won't make you pay.

37:15.950 --> 37:16.560
I have an appointment.

37:16.590 --> 37:17.030
Bye.

37:17.310 --> 37:21.510
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

37:21.760 --> 37:22.620
Are you envious?

37:22.640 --> 37:23.430
No, I'm not.

37:23.570 --> 37:24.320
You're not jealous?

37:24.350 --> 37:25.100
No, I'm not.

37:25.120 --> 37:25.760
I'm envious.

37:28.390 --> 37:29.330
Sorry,

37:29.710 --> 37:30.910
the subscriber you dialed

37:30.930 --> 37:32.300
cannot be connected at the moment.

37:32.470 --> 37:33.630
Please redial later.

37:33.650 --> 37:34.260
Sorry,

37:34.400 --> 37:36.130
the subscriber you dialed

37:36.240 --> 37:38.630
cannot be connected at the moment.

37:37.400 --> 37:39.340
[Calling]

37:38.750 --> 37:40.070
Please redial la—

37:40.300 --> 37:41.430
[Lu Yan]

37:48.250 --> 37:49.160
Sorry,

37:49.530 --> 37:50.830
the subscriber you dialed

37:50.830 --> 37:52.130
cannot be connected at the moment.

37:52.350 --> 37:53.470
Please redial later.

37:53.490 --> 37:54.200
Sorry,

37:54.350 --> 37:55.990
the subscriber you dialed

37:56.110 --> 37:58.410
cannot be connected at the moment.

38:00.140 --> 38:01.150
Sorry,

38:01.230 --> 38:02.530
the subscriber you dialed

38:02.590 --> 38:03.870
cannot be connected at the moment.

38:11.380 --> 38:13.240
[Restaurant is closed]

38:21.010 --> 38:21.850
Who are you looking for?

38:51.240 --> 38:52.170
This is for you.

39:16.990 --> 39:17.460
Thank you.

39:17.510 --> 39:18.030
Okay, thanks.

39:18.880 --> 39:19.700
Try this skewer.

39:19.720 --> 39:20.190
It's so good.

39:20.220 --> 39:20.550
Okay.

39:25.810 --> 39:26.780
Do you like the noodles?

39:27.850 --> 39:28.700
They're great.

39:30.330 --> 39:31.160
Do you come often?

39:32.000 --> 39:33.820
When I get off work late,

39:33.850 --> 39:34.820
I'll get a bowl here.

39:38.940 --> 39:40.260
You know what,

39:40.830 --> 39:41.780
I bet these noodles

39:42.120 --> 39:42.960
are better than

39:42.990 --> 39:43.960
that restaurant's food.

39:43.990 --> 39:44.550
Don't you agree?

39:45.670 --> 39:47.000
Not necessarily.

39:48.700 --> 39:49.920
Isn't this good?

39:49.950 --> 39:50.960
You don't trust me?

39:51.750 --> 39:52.910
Have you eaten there?

39:54.800 --> 39:55.490
No, right?

39:56.150 --> 39:57.050
Me neither.

39:57.730 --> 39:58.320
Since

39:58.350 --> 39:59.630
we've never tried it,

40:00.050 --> 40:01.210
how can we jump to conclusions?

40:01.890 --> 40:03.610
If you really want to bet on it,

40:04.550 --> 40:05.110
how about this?

40:05.500 --> 40:06.310
Next week,

40:06.340 --> 40:07.860
I'll go eat there with you.

40:12.650 --> 40:13.370
Sure.

40:14.640 --> 40:15.160
Okay.

40:16.410 --> 40:17.070
But

40:17.090 --> 40:18.580
next week...

40:19.130 --> 40:21.020
who knows if we'll work overtime again?

40:22.040 --> 40:23.620
Forget about next week then.

40:24.090 --> 40:24.970
Let's just...

40:26.290 --> 40:27.760
get together

40:28.130 --> 40:29.010
anytime.

40:43.510 --> 40:44.310
Delicious.

40:47.920 --> 40:49.480
Do you often get called back

40:50.090 --> 40:50.780
to work

40:50.780 --> 40:51.910
so suddenly like this?

40:52.160 --> 40:53.220
More or less.

40:53.310 --> 40:55.870
It was an unexpected emergency today.

40:55.890 --> 40:56.490
But...

40:57.420 --> 40:58.510
if the hospital

40:58.530 --> 40:59.770
has a sudden operation,

40:59.820 --> 41:01.160
I have to...

41:01.470 --> 41:02.370
stay throughout.

41:04.290 --> 41:05.220
How tough.

41:09.470 --> 41:10.840
I remember you said you wanted to

41:10.870 --> 41:12.070
be a police officer.

41:12.540 --> 41:14.660
Now that your dream has come true...

41:16.390 --> 41:17.300
how do you like it?

41:18.590 --> 41:19.830
When I was young,

41:21.100 --> 41:22.740
I thought criminal police

41:22.990 --> 41:24.020
were super cool

41:24.580 --> 41:25.370
and awesome.

41:25.900 --> 41:27.460
But now that

41:27.510 --> 41:29.350
I'm in the police force, I realized

41:29.370 --> 41:30.610
that's not what it is.

41:32.220 --> 41:33.830
This job comes with many responsibilities,

41:34.030 --> 41:34.990
and

41:35.160 --> 41:37.950
it's more dangerous than I thought.

41:42.290 --> 41:42.890
Is it tiring?

41:44.040 --> 41:44.780
No.

41:46.220 --> 41:46.800
You?

41:48.600 --> 41:49.540
Me neither.

41:50.480 --> 41:51.590
I think

41:52.720 --> 41:55.330
I quite enjoy being a doctor.

41:56.640 --> 41:57.950
So since

41:58.190 --> 41:59.200
we've both found

41:59.230 --> 42:00.600
a calling that's fulfilling to us,

42:00.980 --> 42:01.850
let's toast to that,

42:01.920 --> 42:02.770
Dr. Lu.

42:04.910 --> 42:05.640
Cheers,

42:05.930 --> 42:06.790
Captain Jiang.

42:34.150 --> 42:36.520
[Public Security]

42:41.610 --> 42:42.620
Gather around.

42:42.710 --> 42:43.350
Director Xing.

42:43.370 --> 42:44.830
I'll just say a few words.

42:45.770 --> 42:46.700
First,

42:47.620 --> 42:49.640
the explosion case was resolved perfectly.

42:49.850 --> 42:50.760
The higher-ups

42:50.790 --> 42:51.800
awarded our unit with

42:52.220 --> 42:53.730
a collective third-class merit!

42:57.480 --> 43:00.190
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

42:58.000 --> 42:59.400
Second,

42:59.420 --> 43:01.120
let's welcome Jiang Chengyi.

43:01.790 --> 43:02.540
Applause!

43:02.560 --> 43:03.890
Welcome, welcome!

43:03.910 --> 43:05.090
-Welcome!
-Welcome!

43:04.620 --> 43:09.040
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

43:05.110 --> 43:06.460
-Welcome!
-Welcome!

43:07.900 --> 43:09.260
Third...

43:09.680 --> 43:11.630
Director Xing bought everyone milk tea!

43:12.430 --> 43:13.550
Let me tell you.

43:13.570 --> 43:14.240
Captain Jiang

43:14.280 --> 43:15.660
was my senior at school.

43:15.680 --> 43:16.990
We were classmates.

43:17.150 --> 43:17.750
Work hard.

43:17.780 --> 43:18.640
Don't worry, Director Xing.

43:19.190 --> 43:19.710
Have some milk tea.

43:19.710 --> 43:20.110
Okay.

43:23.200 --> 43:23.880
Come on.

43:24.110 --> 43:24.740
Take one.

43:24.880 --> 43:25.320
Here.

43:25.680 --> 43:26.270
Captain Jiang.

43:26.300 --> 43:26.870
Here's the

43:26.910 --> 43:27.900
retrieval notice you requested.

43:28.430 --> 43:29.350
Okay, thank you.

43:29.410 --> 43:30.600
What case are you working on?

43:31.370 --> 43:32.650
If you're free, come with me tonight.

43:32.670 --> 43:33.590
Okay, let's go.

43:37.320 --> 43:40.680
[Outpatient]

43:40.060 --> 43:41.300
I'm exhausted.

43:41.390 --> 43:42.340
Work's finally over.

43:42.880 --> 43:43.870
I'm sleeping

43:43.960 --> 43:45.070
the minute I get home.

43:46.330 --> 43:48.250
There really were many operations today.

43:48.850 --> 43:49.950
My bike is fixed.

43:50.000 --> 43:50.990
I'm getting it later.

43:51.010 --> 43:51.760
See you.

43:51.790 --> 43:52.910
How about I drive you there?

43:53.100 --> 43:53.870
No need.

43:53.870 --> 43:54.870
I can walk there.

43:55.420 --> 43:56.210
Congrats then.

43:56.630 --> 43:57.510
You won't have to

43:57.530 --> 43:58.430
walk to work anymore.

43:58.470 --> 43:59.550
Right? I'll get going.

44:00.250 --> 44:01.270
You sure you don't want a ride?

44:01.270 --> 44:01.750
No.

44:02.570 --> 44:03.300
Bye.

44:24.180 --> 44:25.090
Mr. Feng.

44:25.200 --> 44:26.480
How's my bike?

44:26.790 --> 44:27.690
Dr. Lu, you're here.

44:27.710 --> 44:28.470
It's not fixed yet.

44:28.470 --> 44:29.110
Wait a moment.

44:29.130 --> 44:29.670
Okay.

44:29.700 --> 44:30.750
I'll check it for you.

44:37.710 --> 44:39.540
What's wrong with it?

44:39.830 --> 44:41.100
The tires are a bit tight.

44:41.200 --> 44:42.570
I'll fix it. Loosen them.

44:42.600 --> 44:43.240
Okay.

44:43.280 --> 44:44.550
Then it'll be less tiring to ride it.

44:53.080 --> 44:54.100
It's getting cold.

44:54.120 --> 44:54.970
Right?

45:00.070 --> 45:00.990
Here's all the surveillance footage

45:01.030 --> 45:01.870
from that day.

45:04.720 --> 45:05.950
Let me see.

45:14.090 --> 45:15.120
Can you zoom in?

45:15.270 --> 45:16.010
Yes.

45:17.350 --> 45:18.510
There are no cameras in the alleys;

45:18.550 --> 45:19.630
the footage is from the main road

45:19.630 --> 45:20.510
by the alley entrance.

45:28.300 --> 45:29.450
Who is this, Jiang?

45:31.670 --> 45:33.200
Someone who shouldn't have appeared.

45:42.930 --> 45:43.870
Go back and check

45:43.870 --> 45:45.070
the cameras around Binjiang Road

45:45.090 --> 45:46.560
for that same person.

45:46.580 --> 45:47.760
Okay, I'll get going.

45:47.980 --> 45:48.520
Okay.

46:02.900 --> 46:03.790
Hello?

46:04.100 --> 46:04.940
What's up?

46:05.050 --> 46:07.520
[Jiang Chengyi]

46:05.240 --> 46:06.300
Are you off work?

46:07.350 --> 46:08.980
I just got off work. I'm on my way home.

46:09.010 --> 46:10.240
I just got my bike.

46:10.620 --> 46:11.770
I just checked

46:11.790 --> 46:12.930
the surveillance footage.

46:13.870 --> 46:15.150
The person you met that day

46:15.170 --> 46:16.710
does look a lot like Deng Man.

46:17.750 --> 46:18.870
Something's off.

46:22.430 --> 46:23.310
Where are you?

46:23.470 --> 46:24.450
I'm in your neighborhood.

46:24.470 --> 46:25.410
Let's meet up.

46:26.400 --> 46:28.750
I'm at the alley by my apartment building.

46:34.500 --> 46:35.200
What's wrong?

46:36.820 --> 46:37.270
Hello?

46:38.210 --> 46:38.870
Lu Yan?

46:39.630 --> 46:40.180
What’s wrong?

46:51.450 --> 46:52.280
What do you want?
